WEBVTT

00:01.016 --> 00:02.664
<i>- Previously on Gotham...</i>
- Hello.

00:02.719 --> 00:04.312
- What's wrong with you?
- I let him out of his cage,

00:04.382 --> 00:06.317
and he helped me get out of mine.

00:06.379 --> 00:08.562
- You're him, the Riddler.
- Hi, Lee.

00:10.388 --> 00:11.520
Butch?

00:12.294 --> 00:13.893
You're alive.

00:13.996 --> 00:17.530
Oh, Butch, I tried.

00:17.633 --> 00:19.266
GILZEAN: Tabby, I'm gonna find a way

00:19.368 --> 00:21.668
to get back to the old me. I promise.

00:21.770 --> 00:23.345
GORDON: Tell me
about your mother, Jerome.

00:23.370 --> 00:24.314
Did she have any enemies?

00:24.339 --> 00:26.172
- No.
- Do you have any other family?

00:26.275 --> 00:28.241
The circus is my family.

00:28.343 --> 00:30.543
JEROME: Now, to free
the rest of our cronies

00:30.646 --> 00:32.879
and blow this pop stand.

00:32.981 --> 00:34.914
BRUCE: I could have killed
Jerome after he kidnapped me

00:35.017 --> 00:36.249
and I didn't.

00:36.351 --> 00:38.685
Any harm he does now,
I share a part of it.

00:38.787 --> 00:40.520
I saw Jerome tonight.

00:40.622 --> 00:42.722
He was looking for the name of
a school, St. Ignatius.

00:42.824 --> 00:44.257
Stay the hell away from that madman.

00:44.359 --> 00:45.925
I'll see you at St. Ignatius, Jim.

00:46.995 --> 00:48.728
♪ ♪

